posts.message:
### Do you know?
__Big Dipper__ supports [Github](https://github.com) favoured `markdown` as always. So you can post your messages in `markdown` on __*Desmos*__ and display well on __Big Dipper__. This helps you explain ideas well. 

__Desmos__ stores any characters so you can express yourself with Emojis 😎. Or write in your favourable languages 우수한!

You can reply this message by executing

'''
desmoscli tx posts create "You are the one." false --parent-id 46 --from \<your_key> -y 
'''

Or like it by

'''
desmoscli tx posts like 46 --from \<your_key> -y

posts.creator: desmos1fc3mdf0ue2f4suyg5vjj75jtaer0cl0dgqvy6u
